headline: These Stocks Are Moving the Most Today: Nvidia, Tesla, Hecla, Newmont, Nike, Vanda, Corcept, DJT, and More
summary: Nvidia shares rise on reports of strong interest from Chinese customers in the chip maker’s hardware, while Newmont and Hecla Mining decline as precious metals prices tumble.

headline: Silver 10x’d the S&P 500 In 2025 And Refiner Stocks Could Be Next
summary: Silver prices recently broke $83 per oz. before an artificially induced pullback due to COMEX changing its margin requirement rules. The price of silver, driven by escalated demand vs. limited supply, should continue to rise going into 2026. At the time of this writing, silver is up over +154% YTD, vs. 17.5% for the S&P ...
